info: 12/05/2023 16:08:47.379 RelationalEventId.CommandExecuted[20101] (Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command) 
      Executed DbCommand (0ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
      SELECT COUNT(*)
      FROM "Show" AS "s"
info: 12/05/2023 16:08:47.394 RelationalEventId.CommandExecuted[20101] (Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command) 
      Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
      SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."AverageRuntime", "s"."DvdCountry", "s"."Ended", "s"."Genres", "s"."IdSchedule", "s"."Language", "s"."Name", "s"."OfficialSite", "s"."Premiered", "s"."Rating", "s"."Runtime", "s"."Status", "s"."Summary", "s"."Type", "s"."Updated", "s"."Url", "s"."WebChannel", "s"."Weight", "s"."idExternals", "s"."idImage", "s"."idLink", "s"."idNetwork", "n"."Id", "n"."Name", "n"."OfficialSite", "n"."idCountry", "c"."Id", "c"."Code", "c"."Name", "c"."Timezone", "s0"."Id", "s0"."Days", "s0"."Time", "e"."Id", "e"."Imdb", "e"."Thetvdb", "e"."Tvrage", "i"."Id", "i"."Medium", "i"."Original", "l"."Id", "l"."PreviousepisodeHref", "l"."SelfHref"
      FROM "Show" AS "s"
      LEFT JOIN "Network" AS "n" ON "s"."idNetwork" = "n"."Id"
      LEFT JOIN "Country" AS "c" ON "n"."idCountry" = "c"."Id"
      LEFT JOIN "Schedule" AS "s0" ON "s"."IdSchedule" = "s0"."Id"
      LEFT JOIN "Externals" AS "e" ON "s"."idExternals" = "e"."Id"
